HEADWORD: Sweet
<hw>Sweet</hw>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To sweeten.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Udall.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

